entrance
This is a big entrance. It's intimidating. Seta is there too, waiting for your return.
It's here that your journey begins. Alongside your trustworthy Seta, the animal who carried you here and your best companion you contemplate the infamous Ronko Ruins. It is said to hold the secret of an ancient medecine. You will need it to save the people of the village you grew in ! Adventurer, mysteries awaits !